      "term": "annulment",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "C1",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "the official act of saying that a law, agreement, or decision is no longer valid",
          "examples": [
            "The court ordered the annulment of the unfair contract.",
            "Consumer groups welcomed the annulment of the new tax rules."
